{"tid":1064343,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實整容嘅人係咪諗住斷六親？","createTime":"2019-03-16T12:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T14:44:22.000Z","uid":216662,"like":26,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dc9ae520356e85eedd35e88ced4f44237ac34b09","tid":1064343,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T12:50:57.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺銅鑼灣等緊人嘅時候， 有個白滑大眼女仔問我係咪萊斯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我：邊位？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢：咁都唔認得～中學同學xx呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我：xx?佢又肥又黑你冒認佢做乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢：屌你！ 冇見咁耐都係咁撚搞笑嘅你（屌你呢兩個字大聲到幾乎全銅鑼灣都聽到）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我： 成條街都知你想屌我啦，咁你想點呀小姐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢：我個fd未到， 不如去飲杯嘢傾下大家近況吖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我： 咁不如傾下啲人點解要整容吖。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢立即黑面扮打電話，話過朋友到咗下次再傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後佢走嗰陣我補咗句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 你以前靚好多，bye<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d2a837d2edaa879023721681a7b94cf121361f","tid":1064343,"uid":198583,"like":34,"dislike":6,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T12:59:32.000Z","msg":"整容有咩問題"},{"pid":"aeb5cec6d4686f5ae53a160d94ee9888b053e5ec","tid":1064343,"uid":216662,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"88d2a837d2edaa879023721681a7b94cf121361f","tid":1064